    "For multilingual audio (e.g. Japanese) Whisper is usually more reliable than Apple; large-v3 has the best quality but is larger and slower.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "For multilingual audio (e.g. Japanese) Whisper is usually more reliable than Apple; large-v3 has the best quality but is larger and slower."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "多言語(日本語など)では Apple より安定することが多く、large-v3 は最高品質ですが大きく低速です。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "多语(如日语)通常比 Apple 更稳;large-v3 质量最佳但更大更慢。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "多語(如日文)通常比 Apple 更穩;large-v3 品質最佳但較大較慢。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
